## Quality Gates

Run these checks in order before committing:
### Lint
- `cargo clippy -- -D warnings`
- `cargo fmt --check`

### Test
- `cargo test`

### Ci (inferred from workflow)
- `cargo build --verbose`
- `cargo fmt --all --check`
- `cargo check`
## Security

